import React from 'react'
import { View, Text } from 'react-native'
import Layout from '../components/Layout'

const TaskFormScreen = () => {
    return (
        <Layout>
            <TextInput
                placeholder="Write a title"
            />
            <TextInput
                placeholder="Write a description"
            />
        </Layout>
    )
}

export default TaskFormScreen
